metadata.name: Bingy Bongy - BB01
metadata.description: Great Odin’s raven! BB01 NFT features Bingy Bongy Anchorman, who wants you to know that he is very important and has many leather-bound books. Enjoy that smile as he confidently reads the news. Let’s just hope that it’s on the teleprompter. Stay classy and collect all 5 to own the entire collection. This official Bingy Bongy original NFT by Roy Husdell began as a playful exploration and will soon evolve to include a collection of customizable Bingy Bongy vinyl figures.
